sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / API Client
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Reconciler as TrainJobReconciler<br/>(controller-runtime)
    participant RuntimeFW as Runtime Framework<br/>(Plugin Chain)
    participant TrainingPod as Training Pod rank-0<br/>28080/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,TrainingPod: Flow 1: TrainJob Creation and Resource Provisioning

    User->>K8sAPI: POST TrainJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / Client Cert
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-trainer-...-trainjob<br/>TLS Client Cert
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Allowed
    K8sAPI-->>User: TrainJob Created
    K8sAPI->>Reconciler: Watch Event (TrainJob)<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Reconciler->>RuntimeFW: Resolve Runtime + Build Resources
    RuntimeFW-->>Reconciler: JobSet, PodGroup, Secrets, ConfigMaps
    Reconciler->>K8sAPI: Create JobSet<br/>ServiceAccount Bearer Token
    Reconciler->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy (RHOAI)<br/>ServiceAccount Bearer Token
    Reconciler->>K8sAPI: Create PodGroup (if Volcano/CoScheduling)<br/>ServiceAccount Bearer Token
    Reconciler->>K8sAPI: Create SSH Secret + Hostfile CM (if MPI)<br/>ServiceAccount Bearer Token

    Note over User,TrainingPod: Flow 2: RHAI Progression Tracking (RHOAI)

    loop Every 30s (configurable 5s-300s)
        Reconciler->>K8sAPI: List Pods (APIReader direct call)<br/>ServiceAccount Bearer Token
        K8sAPI-->>Reconciler: Pod list with status
        Reconciler->>TrainingPod: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP plaintext (NetworkPolicy enforced)
        TrainingPod-->>Reconciler: Training metrics JSON
        Reconciler->>K8sAPI: PATCH TrainJob annotations<br/>ServiceAccount Bearer Token
    end

    Note over User,TrainingPod: Flow 3: Distributed PyTorch Training (inter-pod)

    participant Worker as Trainer Node (worker)
    participant Master as Trainer Node rank-0 (master)<br/>29500/TCP

    Worker->>Master: TCP rendezvous<br/>Port 29500/TCP plaintext
    Worker->>Worker: NCCL all-reduce<br/>Dynamic ports, plaintext<br/>(same-job NetworkPolicy)

    Note over User,TrainingPod: Flow 4: MPI Distributed Training (inter-pod)

    participant Launcher as MPI Launcher Pod
    participant MPINode as MPI Node Pods<br/>2222/TCP SSH

    Launcher->>MPINode: SSH connection<br/>Port 2222/TCP<br/>ECDSA P521 key auth
    MPINode->>MPINode: NCCL/MPI collective ops<br/>Dynamic ports, plaintext<br/>(same-job NetworkPolicy)
